This was Eric Clapton's first appearance on Larry King Live.
It may also be the worst job I've ever seen Larry King do on 
an interview.  Clapton looks very uncomfortable -  at times
you will sense that he wants out of the studio as soon as 
possible.  Clearly, Eric was using this forum to promote
The Crossroads Center in Antigua
